@startuml UC-MGR-04: View Department Dashboard

actor "Manager" as Mgr
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "DepartmentController" as API
participant "DepartmentService" as Svc
database "departments / projects / requests" as DB

Mgr -> FE: Chọn "Dashboard phòng ban"
FE -> API: GET /api/v1/departments/me/dashboard
API -> Svc: getDeptDashboard(currentManager)
Svc -> DB: findDeptById(manager.departmentId)
Svc -> DB: findProjectsByDeptId(deptId)
Svc -> DB: findRequestsByDeptId(deptId)
DB --> Svc: Department + projects + requests
Svc --> API: DashboardDTO
API --> FE: 200 DashboardDTO
FE --> Mgr: Hiển thị:\ntotalProjectQuota, totalAvailableBalance,\nDS DA, DS YC phòng ban

@enduml
